<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Clangd on miyan的博客</title><link>https://miyan.site/tags/clangd/</link><description>Recent content in Clangd on miyan的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 May 2025 18:26:21 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://miyan.site/tags/clangd/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>vscode clangd 设置</title><link>https://miyan.site/p/vscode-clangd-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miyan.site/p/vscode-clangd-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>禁用microsoft c++插件的提示
打开vscode的设置界面，搜索&lt;code>c++ engine&lt;/code>，选择&lt;code>C_Cpp.intelliSenseEngine&lt;/code>，设置为&lt;code>disabled&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对应的settings.json设置为&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;C_Cpp.intelliSenseEngine&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;disabled&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>添加clangd参数&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>不自动添加头文件&lt;/li>
&lt;li>补全时不自动填写函数参数&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>打开vscode的设置界面，搜索&lt;code>clangd arguments&lt;/code>，选择&lt;code>clangd.arguments&lt;/code>，点击&lt;code>Add Item&lt;/code>添加对应参数。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对应的settings.json设置为&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;clangd.arguments&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--header-insertion=never&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;--function-arg-placeholders=0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item></channel></rss>